"Today we proudly present the official beta release of [Castmill](https://castmill.com), the online digital advertisement platform. Castmill makes it easy for anyone to benefit from digital advertisement and information. No expensive hardware of software is required. A PC, laptop, tablet or Smart TV with an HTML5 capable web browser and and internet connection is all that it takes. Castmill is free to use for screen owners and will soon open up for paying advertisers as well. For more information see the Press Release in [English](/docs/pr_castmill_beta_en.pdf) or [Swedish](/docs/pr_castmill_beta_se.pdf)"
